data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Clarksville! This charming abode offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. The garage has been thoughtfully converted into the perfect second living space, offering endless possibilities for use, whether it's a cozy family room, a home office, or a playroom. The heart of this home is the beautifully appointed kitchen, featuring granite countertops and a spacious eat-in area bathed in natural light. Step outside to your private, fenced-in backyard equipped with a generous shed, offering ample storage space for all your outdoor gear and tools. Live free in the absence of HOA restrictions, giving you the independence to personalize your space and enjoy it to the fullest. Plus, with easy access to Fort Campbell gates, commuting is a breeze!
